songs.title: Same Niggas*
songs.lyrics:
[Chorus: Quavo, Gunna & Future]
...I brought the curve and she came out the dirt (Dirt, dirt)
Gang come first, make it work-work-work (Work, work, work)
Empty out the clip, make 'em jump out the shirt (Shooter shirt)
Drop top, I'm goin' then I jump out the vert (Wheezy outta here)
